來看。（香港人的）創意行動沒有政治訴求是不會發展的。所以這個獎項不只讚揚香港人的創意，也是讚揚他們的勇氣。"},{"pid":"2830cad3dd363e264f4d1bf5d8be779d05f38e12","tid":2066285,"uid":241504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T07:46:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"809f0ee4eb6150f64f82991fcb65bf865fc913c8","tid":2066285,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T07:46:57.000Z","msg":"入去多謝人：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/arselectronica/posts/10159620602199918\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Farselectronica%2Fposts%2F10159620602199918&d=St%2FdMm9ieZWtYGJEeV6aa6HX%2F1llhPerIglyOgZNoj0%3D&h=47281d05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/arselectronica/posts/10159620602199918</a>"},{"pid":"a0e8e2c95ef953258be02b779f6bb08a715772fe","tid":2066285,"uid":38620,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T07:49:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ars.electronica.art/prix/en/winners/#digitalcommunities\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fars.electronica.art%2Fprix%2Fen%2Fwinners%2F%23digitalcommunities&d=St%2FdMm9ieZWtYGJEeV6aa6HX%2F1llhPerIglyOgZNoj0%3D&h=41b29d9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ars.electronica.art/prix/en/winners/#digitalcommunities</a><br />\n<br />\n英文原文喺度 <br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n&ldquo;The protest movement is leaderless, and this decentralization results in massive online and organic tactics using platforms like <span style=\"color: red;\">LIHKG</span>&mdash;a local, lo-fi version of Reddit where users can communicate and vote on posts&mdash;or AirDrop to share campaign messages&rdquo;"},{"pid":"f969bf124f9f2818b4302d4dc274fd349735e564","tid":2066285,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T07:49:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0acd6946ea300b14492e74b89e48db12c46e71a","tid":2066285,"uid":3560,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T07:52:51.000Z","msg":"睇到段新聞第一個反應係多謝Ars Electronica咁勇敢可以公開屌支那<br />\n畢竟Ars Electronica作爲一個旅遊景點每年都應該幾多支那人去<br />\n<br />\n兩秒之後，發現可以公開屌支那，嗰種免於恐懼說心中真話嘅言論自由，其實係好正常。<br />\n<br />\n連我自己都開始有自我審查嘅潛意識 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8671a89bf94823a0911e1a11a329c7978f7c5f0","tid":2066285,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T07:58:09.000Z","msg":"好快搞鳩埋IT呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac084f856ca5ce42955dc1ab62295da28fc9a711","tid":2066285,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8671a89bf94823a0911e1a11a329c7978f7c5f0","tid":2066285,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T07:58:09.000Z","msg":"好快搞鳩埋IT呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T08:00:57.000Z","msg":"你覺得本身創科局冇搞到？<br />\n之前黑警都有搞tg group"},{"pid":"bec783d68714fdd3b09a4bfeefb58532d85b8265","tid":2066285,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T08:02:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c70c7013bad16f888c521fe6192ee6f58a3c4f1b","tid":2066285,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T08:07:15.000Z","msg":"Hongkongers<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"064073d0100dd8c208ff0460a7ab880ea4a475a8","tid":2066285,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"